======
kmrviz
======

KMRViz is a visualization tool that visualizes traces of a KMR (MapReduce for K supercomputer) program as timelines of processes (nodes/ranks).

=============
Prerequisites
=============

KMRViz is dependant on:

- GTK+3 library - a cross-platform GUI toolkit: although GTK+ 3.0 is almost ok a version >= 3.10 is recommended (GTK+ 2 is not compatible)
  Ubuntu 14.04: libgtk-3-dev package
